Subject: VIA PadLock crypto accelerator driver
From: Michal Ludvig <mludvig@suse.cz>
Patch-mainline: 2.6.10-bk1

Driver for VIA PadLock on-chip crypto accelerator. For now it 
can speed-up the AES algorithm on processors VIA Nehemiah.

